==Chart performance==
As of August, 2010, "If I Had You" has sold 302,000 downloads<ref>http://content.usatoday.com/communities/idolchatter/post/2010/08/idol-track-sales-adam-lambert-carrie-underwood-daughtry-1/1?loc=interstitialskip</ref> in the United States and charted at #32 on the [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]]. As of July 22, 2010, "If I Had You" has reached the top 10 in Canada, New Zealand, Australia and Finland.

